  "text": "Elephants are known to forage widely beyond the boundaries of protected areas and enter into cultivated crop farms. This cropraiding behaviour is a risk factor [CITATION_1] that frequently causes conflicts and results in elephant injury (physical injury or death) [CITATION_2] .",
